	<h1 class="title">里约奥运会还有大半年，新浪已经吆喝开了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">叶芳妤</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-11 13:23:22 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18899/medium/18899.jpg?1449798732" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


